Nishal Surname (Gotra in Hindi) comes under the caste Brahmin , sub caste Jangra Brahmin. They are the descendents of Rishi Angira ([[Angiras (sage)]]). The word Jangra comes from the name of Rishi [[Angiras (sage)]] also called as Rishi Jangira.

Etymology : in Hindi, Nishal means endless, which has no end, Lord [[Shiva]],

[[Category:Surname]]
